author: Heather Barrett
title: GreyJay didn't expect his new album to be so relevant
description: GreyJay's album Wholesome Prison Blues takes on a literal meaning during these days of COVID-19-related physical distancing, self-isolation and quarantining.
content:
GreyJay, also known as Jordan Young, wasn't expecting his album Wholesome Prison Blues to be quite so relevant.
